    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay, i didnt know about that reye's thing. that sounds scary. i think i actually have some infantil ibuprofen here too though... if i can't do aspirin is a dose of ibuprofen okay for an 8 year old? how much should i give him for a fever?",
